Ah, I see! There's already **`middleware.ts`** protecting all routes:

```typescript
// middleware.ts checks for valid JWT on ALL routes except:
// - /api/auth/*
// - /_next/*
// - /auth/signin

// /api/jobs gets caught by this check:
const token = await getToken({ req, secret: process.env.NEXTAUTH_SECRET });
if (!token) {
  return NextResponse.redirect(signInUrl);
